title: Laura Ingraham Podcast April 18,2016
description:
THE LAURA INGRAHAM SHOW PODCAST april 18,2016

CA Campaign Chairman: 'I don't think Trump will be the nominee; I know the type of people that go to the convention in July' 

Ron Nehring - National Spokesman and CA Campaign Chairman, Ted Cruz for President
Wendy Long - Litigation attorney; Nominee for the Republican Senate seat in NY against Chuck Schumer
Abby Johnson - Pro-life activist who previously worked at Planned Parenthood as a clinic director
